docs.lead_paragraph: AFTER a year at the head of Ontario's overwhelmingly Liberal government, Mitchell F. Hepburn, 38-year-old Premier of Canada's most popular Province, remains the most interesting figure on the Canadian political scene.

headline.main: A NEW POLITICAL STAR RISES IN CANADA; Hepburn, Who Revived The Liberal Party In Ontario, Plays A National Role
